Title: Fisher-Hartwig conjecture and the correlators in XY spin chain
Authors: An.A.Ovchinnikov
Categories: math-ph hep-th math.MP nlin.SI
Comments: LaTex, 10 pages
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett.A366:357-362,2007
DOI: 10.1016/j.physleta.2007.02.061
\\
  We apply the theorems from the theory of Toeplitz determinants to calculate
the asymptotics of the correlators in the XY spin chain in the transverse
magnetic field. The asymptotics of the correlators for the XX spin chain in the
magnetic field are obtained.
